git gui difftool is a script using in git-gui,make it easy to use visual diff tool in git-gui.

install & setting
run these commands:
 git clone git://github.com/zhangchunlin/gitguidifftool.git
 cd gitguidifftool
 .\git_gui_difftool.py

usage
-git gui
-click at the file you want to visual diff
-menu->Tools->the menu you just setting
